 - As a result of increased engagement, NHS England now play a more active role at regional level, taking ownership to influence customer behaviours across STPs to help drive migration pace more effectively, and HSCN Programme Board membership now includes regional NHS England digital transformation leads.
 - A tail management strategy including tactical solutions, migration acceleration support and BT interim solutions are in place to drive an August 2020 completion, supporting customers at risk of not migrating by August. The programme have also successfully negotiated a Year 4 extension to the Transition Network providing contingency to March 2021.

